OL,5,Crun
OL,7,FA painter and decorator who drove into
OL,8,Fa group of people to avenge his son
OL,9,Fwhile he was high on drink and drugs
OL,10,Fhas been jailed for a minimum of 32
OL,11,Fyears for murdering a much-loved
OL,12,Fgrandfather.
OL,14,FMartin Breeze, 57, swerved off the
OL,15,Froad and smashed into a group who had
OL,16,Fbeen in a disagreement with his son
OL,17,FShaun Breeze, 30, who had gone out to
OL,18,Fbuy drugs.
