OL,3,CFather 'likely' to die in prison as he
OL,4,Cand son jailed for 'revenge' hit-and-
OL,5,Crun
OL,7,FBrian Darby, 60, a popular and hard-
OL,8,Fworking project manager with the RSPB,
OL,9,Fwas carried on the front of the bonnet
OL,10,Fof Martin Breeze's Citroen Berlingo
OL,11,Fbefore falling on to the carriageway
OL,12,Fsome distance from the impact.
OL,14,FHe died at the scene in Ingelby
OL,15,FBarwick, on Teesside, at 11.30pm on 9
OL,16,FFebruary last year.
OL,18,FThe van also collided with Kelly
OL,19,FJordan, who almost died, and two other
OL,20,Fyoung men, Teesside Crown Court heard.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/14
