OL,5,Crun
OL,7,FBoth were convicted of perverting the
OL,8,Fcourse of justice regarding the claim
OL,9,Fthat the van had been stolen.
OL,11,FMr Justice Jacobs sentenced Martin
OL,12,FBreeze to life with a minimum term of
OL,13,F32 years and said the defendant may
OL,14,Fwell die in prison.
OL,16,FShaun Breeze, who was diagnosed with
OL,17,Fanxiety from childhood, was jailed for
OL,18,F16 years.
