OL,7,FThe son had been on his bike looking
OL,8,Fto buy drugs when he encountered Mr
OL,9,FDarby's group of friends, who had
OL,10,Fenjoyed a pleasant night out at a
OL,11,Flocal pub.
OL,13,FShaun Breeze argued with the group
OL,14,Fafter he almost rode into one of them
OL,15,Fand was chased away, later dumping his
OL,16,Fbike.
OL,18,FHe rang his father, who drove out to
OL,19,Fpick him up, despite being drunk, on
OL,20,Fdrugs and uninsured.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/14
