OL,7,FOn the way home, Shaun Breeze pointed
OL,8,Fout the group with whom he had
OL,9,Fdisagreed and his father pulled off
OL,10,Fthe road and deliberately ploughed
OL,11,Finto them.
OL,13,FThe prosecution said the father and
OL,14,Fson were out for "revenge".
OL,16,FLater that evening Shaun Breeze made a
OL,17,F999 call to police in an apparent
OL,18,Feffort to clear his father's name and
OL,19,Fto report the van as having been
OL,20,Fstolen, which was not true.
