OL,7,FShaun Breeze made a 999 call to
OL,8,FCleveland Police in a bid to 'clear'
OL,9,Fhis father's name and to report his
OL,10,Fvan as stolen
OL,12,FMr Darby was a nature-loving family
OL,13,Fman who lit up every room he entered,
OL,14,Fhis daughter said in a victim
OL,15,Fstatement.
OL,17,FShe expressed "the deep and profound
OL,18,Fsadness" in the lives of family,
OL,19,Fadding that "a light has been switched
OL,20,Foff and there is now no enjoyment in
OL,21,Fanything".
