OL,7,FCCTV footage released by Cleveland
OL,8,FPolice captures Martin Breeze driving
OL,9,Fto pick up his son Shaun Breeze before
OL,10,Fthe pair then sought out the group of
OL,11,Ffriends
OL,13,FShe also told the court that her scars
OL,14,Fwere a physical reminder of the events
OL,15,Fof 9 February last year and she still
OL,16,Fsuffered recurring nightmares and had
OL,17,Fspeech problems.
