OL,7,FWalking with a crutch to the witness
OL,8,Fbox, she told the court: "I have lost
OL,9,Fparts of my life that I enjoyed most `
OL,10,FI can't go to the gym, I can't walk
OL,11,Fthe dog, socialise and can't go on
OL,12,Fholiday.
OL,14,F"My 50th birthday party was cancelled
OL,15,Fbecause I was ill.
OL,17,F"These things have been taken away due
OL,18,Fto the reckless actions of Shaun and
OL,19,FMartin Breeze."
