OL,7,FDavid Lamb KC, for Martin Breeze, said
OL,8,Fhis client had no previous convictions
OL,9,Fand was testing negative for drugs
OL,10,Fwhile on remand.
OL,12,FJohn Elvidge KC, for Shaun Breeze,
OL,13,Fsaid his client had been diagnosed as
OL,14,Fbeing on the autism spectrum prior to
OL,15,Fthe offence and also had no previous
OL,16,Fconvictions.
OL,18,FMr Elvidge said Shaun Breeze used
OL,19,Fillegal drugs to mitigate his anxiety.
