OL,7,FSenior Investigating Officer Detective
OL,8,FInspector Matt Hollingsworth, from
OL,9,FCleveland Police's Homicide and Major
OL,10,FEnquiry Team, said: "It's almost
OL,11,Fbeyond comprehension that a chance
OL,12,Fencounter between a group of friends
OL,13,Fand Shaun Breeze would be the catalyst
OL,14,Ffor such a senseless and callous
OL,15,Fattack.
OL,17,F"Martin and Shaun Breeze killed a well-
OL,18,Fknown and well-liked man as well as
OL,19,Finjuring or trying to injure others in
OL,20,Fthe group purely as an act of revenge.
