OL,7,F"As we heard from the impact
OL,8,Fstatements read out in court, this
OL,9,Fattack has had such a devastating
OL,10,Fimpact on the victims, their family,
OL,11,Fand their friends.
OL,13,F"I know today's sentencing will never
OL,14,Fbring Brian back or lessen the
OL,15,Fphysical and psychological pain
OL,16,Fsuffered by all those impacted by this
OL,17,Fattack; however I hope it begins to
OL,18,Fprovide some form of closure to know
OL,19,Fthe men responsible for this will be
OL,20,Fin prison for a very long time.
